<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
  <head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <title>楽アド - キャンペーン審査通過</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      color: #74787e;
      font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;
      height: 100%;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
      width: 100% !important;
    "
    bgcolor="#f2f4f6"
  >
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        width: 100% !important;
        height: 100%;
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1.6;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: #74787e;
        -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;
      }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .email-body_inner {
          width: 100% !important;
        }
      }
    </style>

    <table
      class="email-wrapper"
      width="100%"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; width: 100%;"
      bgcolor="#f2f4f6"
    >
      <tr>
        <td align="center" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; word-break: break-word">
          <table
            class="email-content"
            width="100%"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; width: 100%;"
          >
            <tr>
              <td
                class="email-masthead"
                style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 25px 0; word-break: break-word; background-color: #0ea5e9;"
                align="center"
                bgcolor="#0ea5e9"
              >
                <a
                  href="{{product_url}}"
                  style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #facc15; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;"
                >{{product_name}}</a>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td
                class="email-body"
                width="100%"
                cellpadding="0"
                cellspacing="0"
                style="
                  border-bottom: 1px solid #edeff2;
                  border-top: 1px solid #edeff2;
                  box-sizing: border-box;
                  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                  margin: 0;
                  padding: 0;
                  width: 100%;
                "
                bgcolor="#ffffff"
              >
                <table
                  class="email-body_inner"
                  align="center"
                  width="570"
                  cellpadding="0"
                  cellspacing="0"
                  style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0; width: 570px;"
                  bgcolor="#ffffff"
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      class="content-cell"
                      style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 35px; word-break: break-word;"
                    >
                      <div style="font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', Arial, sans-serif; color: #2c3e50;">

                        <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">{{contactName}}様</p>

                        <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">この度は楽アドにキャンペーンをご出稿いただき、誠にありがとうございます。</p>

                        <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">お申込みいただきましたキャンペーンの審査が完了し、<strong>配信開始</strong>となりましたことをお知らせいたします。</p>

                        <table
                          style="background-color: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; border-radius: 6px; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 20px 0; width: 100%;"
                          cellpadding="0"
                          cellspacing="0"
                        >
                          <tr>
                            <td style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #166534; font-size: 14px; padding-bottom: 6px;">
                              <strong>キャンペーン名：</strong> {{campaignName}}
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                          <tr>
                            <td style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #166534; font-size: 14px;">
                              <strong>ステータス：</strong> 配信中
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                        </table>

                        <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">キャンペーンの配信状況はダッシュボードからご確認いただけます。</p>

                        <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; text-align: center;">
                          <a
                            href="{{product_url}}/dashboard/advertiser/campaigns"
                            style="
                              background-color: #0ea5e9;
                              border-radius: 4px;
                              color: #ffffff;
                              display: inline-block;
                              font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                              font-size: 15px;
                              font-weight: bold;
                              padding: 12px 30px;
                              text-decoration: none;
                            "
                          >キャンペーンを確認する</a>
                        </p>

                        <p style="margin: 20px 0 0 0;">ご不明な点がございましたら、お気軽にお問い合わせください。</p>

                        <p style="margin: 20px 0 0 0;">今後ともよろしくお願いいたします。</p>

                        <p style="margin: 20px 0 0 0;">合同会社はと<br>堀田</p>

                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; word-break: break-word">
                <table
                  class="email-footer"
                  align="center"
                  width="570"
                  cellpadding="0"
                  cellspacing="0"
                  style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0; text-align: center; width: 570px;"
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td
                      align="center"
                      style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 35px; word-break: break-word;"
                    >
                      <p style="color: #aeaeae; font-size: 12px; margin: 0;">
                        &copy; {{company_name}}. All rights reserved.
                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
